            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>由著名的日系 RPG 遊戲《女神異聞錄 5》，故事是講述在學生與偷心怪盜的雙重生活下，讓大人悔改的拯救劇情，其後並指出《皇家版》加強內容與及延伸作品《亂戰》。而最近 Sega ATLUS 推出以策略戰棋 RPG 為主要的《女神異聞錄 5 戰略版》。遊戲不但有著全新的玩法，而且還是會保留「1MORE」、「總攻擊」等戰鬥元素。遊戲正式於 11 月 17 日正式發售，其中支援 Xbox Series X|S 及 One、PlayStation 4 / 5、Nintendo Switch 以及 PC 平台，並在首日加入 Xbox Game Pass。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206462 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全新遊戲類型</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206471" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-32-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-32-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-32-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-32.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲風格延續前作</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206478" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-17-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-17-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-17-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-17.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新角色登場</p><h2><span class="s1">故事加插在舊作，遊玩前重温免疑惑</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">以《女神異聞錄 5 戰略版》故事的時間線，是在《皇家版》中後期之間，如果玩家沒有遊玩此係列的作品，會難免對於遊戲的世界觀感到疑惑。而且遊戲中有著很大量的劇透與及後期內容，遊戲也沒有介紹角色與及遊戲的世界觀，新加入的玩家很難會代入進去遊戲裡，相反可能因為很多事情看不懂而會放棄。相對有認識的玩家，一定會對於《女 5》的角色重新再出現而感到興奮，遊戲還是巧妙地將每個角色的定位帶出來。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206465 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-10-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-10-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-10-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-10.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲曾經出現的角色</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206466" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲許多日常回憶對話</p><h2><span class="s1">可愛化的人物，但保留系列風格</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">雖然人物全部都被可愛化了，變得更 Q 版及偏向兒童向，不過只要遊玩下去就會發覺沒有太大不同。而且不管從人物上，或是從遊戲界面上，都充滿著《女 5》的風格，絕對能讓玩家重新再愛上這風格。而遊戲的劇情非常幽默，如果喜歡看劇情的玩家一定會被裏面的對話會心一笑，遊戲並不是單一隻有文字對話。過場時有著不同的影片讓玩家大呼過癮，而且也是相當多影片讓玩家慢慢欣賞，務求讓玩家在《女神異聞錄 5 戰略版》不會感到無聊。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206463 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有趣人物表情</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206481" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-18-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-18-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-18-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-18.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲介面保留原作風格</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206479" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-22-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-22-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-22-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-22.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可愛而不失霸氣的角色</p><h2><span class="s1">循序漸進的遊戲方式，讓戰鬥慢慢刺激</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">在《女神異聞錄 5 戰略版》的遊玩方式其實與《Mario + Rabbit》系列極為相似，當我以為每個遊戲章節會比較簡單與及不需要太多的操作，結果這次遊戲給我非常深刻的印象。遊戲隨着進度慢慢讓玩家瞭解更多遊戲系統，例如有着擊倒功能、「1more」功能、屬性功能等等，甚至可以利用特定條件使出合力攻擊，讓玩家有更多發揮空間有着更多的可玩性及策略性。雖然元素上沒有相剋效果，不過有着不同的位移或附加傷害，這可以讓玩家有更多有趣的組合去應付適人。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206467 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-7-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-7.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲負面屬性附加</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206468" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-14-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-14-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-14-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-14.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲共同總攻擊</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206480" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-29-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-29-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-29-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-29.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲依舊可運用地形</p><h2><span class="s1">約 100 個人格面具合成</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">隨着玩家完成遊戲，會獲得金色齒輪為獎勵，而金色齒輪則代表着不同的人格面具，只要與不同的人格面具進行合成就有機會獲得新的人格面具。而當中合成可以選擇繼承過往的技能，如果想沿用舊技能就必須從該技能的人格面具着手再合成上去。而當中超過 100 個面具等着玩家去合成，當然等級越高就代表可以加成角色的能力值就越高。除此之外玩家亦可以選擇購買過往曾經合成的人格面具，用咗方便可以分岐更多新人格面具。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206470 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-30-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-30-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-30-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-30.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲多款人格面具</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206477" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-21-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-21-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-21-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-21.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲合成後可選擇繼承技能</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206476" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-20-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-20-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-20-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-20.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可通過商店購買人格面具</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206469" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-31-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-31-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-31-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-31.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲合成新的人格面具</p><h2><span class="s1">團隊等級減輕重刷，但影響深遠</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">這次遊戲是採用團隊等級來代替角色個人等級，不過團隊等級的用途非常廣泛，首先會隨着等級提升近戰傷害。而當中人格面具也要按團隊等級來合成，不能合成超過團隊等級的人格面具。當然每個任務都會有不同條件讓玩家達成，達成越多經驗就越多，玩家可以先輕鬆玩然後重複遊玩該任務來達成條件。沒有角色等級之下玩家只能透過日常對話或支線任務來獲得更多 GP，GP 可以在角色技能樹上強化，從而獲得更好的能力與狀態。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206464 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-28-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-28-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-28-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-28.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲日常對話有機會獲得 GP</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206484" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-23-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-23-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-23-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-23.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支線任務大大影響角色成長度</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206482" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-25-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-25-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-25-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-25.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲獲得大量 GP</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206483" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-27-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-27-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-27-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-27.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲各角色技能樹大同小異</p><h2><span class="s1">總結：保留《女神異聞錄 5》風格的優良作品</span></h2><p class="p1"><span class="s1">比起正傳作品，《女神異聞錄 5 戰略版》相對較為輕鬆以及畫風較為 Q 版而更容易深受玩家喜愛。雖然遊戲內容較為少，不過從遊戲性，系統設計，甚至在背景音樂上也看到製作的用心，足以證明沒有毀掉《女神異聞錄 5》的招牌。而且一貫保留豐富的劇情內容，以及爽快的遊戲流程，即使換上戰棋遊戲能讓玩家融入其中。不管如何，在將近 50 遊戲小時過程中，能夠遊玩《女神異聞錄 5》新作品，結論是非常值得花時間來推薦大家遊玩這個遊戲！</span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206473 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲角色聚首一堂</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206474" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可選擇困難度</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206475" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-13-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-13-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-13-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-13.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲爽快又具戰略性的遊戲</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206472" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-26-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-26-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-26-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/persona5t-26.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲特典送的，很無敵</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

